track_notes:
2.4 mile hike with  EG along the Appalachian Trail. Trailhead is just off of Hwy 25/70 on Lookout Mtn Road (35.910, -82.791). There is a fire tower with an intact cabin (no windows or door) that can provide a unique activation QTH.

Rich Mtn can also be accessed as a drive-up via FS Road 467/Lookout Mtn Rd or a shorter but steeper hike along the AT southbound from Hurricane Gap (estimated 1.1 miles with 930 EG).
track_title: W4C/CM-110 Rich Mtn vi AT from Tanyard Gap
